\section{Spacing}{

By default, \strong{one blank line} is inserted between the last body row and
the first footnote. Control this with \code{\link[=fr_spacing]{fr_spacing()}}:

\if{html}{\out{<div class="sourceCode r">}}\preformatted{spec |> fr_spacing(footnotes_before = 0L)   # no gap
spec |> fr_spacing(footnotes_before = 2L)   # two blank lines
